# Cloud Architecture Center - Regional availability for Cloud Volumes Service on Google Cloud
Last reviewed 2023-11-19 UTC
Cloud Volumes Service for Google Cloud is available in several regions. For details about regional availability see [Cloud Volumes Global Regions for Google Cloud](https://cloud.netapp.com/cloud-volumes-global-regions#cvsGc)
